<h2 id="setting-the-serializationgroup">Setting the SerializationGroup <a class="headerlink" href="conditionally-embedding-relations#setting-the-serializationgroup" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Ok... so now, how can we serialize a specific set of groups? To answer that, open
<code>ProgrammerController</code> and find <code>showAction()</code>. Follow <code>createApiResponse()</code> into the
